Interface WeatherSensor

All Superinterfaces:
ControllerIO, Device, SonarObject
All Known Implementing Classes:
WeatherSensorImpl
public interface WeatherSensor extends Device
A weather sensor is a device for sampling weather data, such as precipitation rates, visibility and wind speed.
Author:
Douglas Lau, Michael Darter, John L. Stanley - SRF Consulting
